b_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/f9270d6a0dc418ba0662c92f6db78e9e.webp?t=1643182215\" width=67 height=5 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/26904ed5ade9c886ee8e2c85302d8198.poster.avif?t=1643182215\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/26904ed5ade9c886ee8e2c85302d8198.webm?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/26904ed5ade9c886ee8e2c85302d8198.mp4?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/444884a36a7cf24afb1c92f481046066.webp?t=1643182215\" width=625 height=50 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">In some levels, you may even need to redefine the rules of the game and win the game based on the rules you just defined. </ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/f9270d6a0dc418ba0662c92f6db78e9e.webp?t=1643182215\" width=67 height=5 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/7bca72e31345eecb21a20b69541b631c.poster.avif?t=1643182215\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/7bca72e31345eecb21a20b69541b631c.webm?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/7bca72e31345eecb21a20b69541b631c.mp4?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/mp4\